---
import DraftLayout from '../../layouts/DraftLayout.astro';
---
<DraftLayout title="Subtle Somatics — Gentle Transformation Within & Beyond" activeNav="home" hasHero={true}>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg">
      <img src="/images/hero.jpg" alt="" loading="eager" fetchpriority="high" />
      <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-content">
      <p class="hero-eyebrow hero-anim" data-anim-order="1">Subtle Somatics</p>
      <h1 class="hero-anim" data-anim-order="2">Come home to the wisdom of your body</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub hero-anim" data-anim-order="3">Presence-based coaching and spinal energetics for those ready to meet themselves at the depth where transformation naturally unfolds.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions hero-anim" data-anim-order="4">
        <a href="#booking" class="btn btn-filled">Book a Free Discovery Call</a>
        <a href="#philosophy" class="btn">Explore</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="scroll-indicator" aria-hidden="true">
      <span class="scroll-text">Scroll</span>
      <svg width="16" height="24" viewBox="0 0 16 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
        <polyline points="3 12 8 17 13 12"></polyline>
      </svg>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About intro -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-image reveal-left">
        <img src="/images/kaja-profile.jpg" alt="Kaja Possert-Bienzle" />
      </div>
      <div class="about-text reveal-right">
        <p class="eyebrow">About Kaja</p>
        <h2>Unfolding companion. Wholeness witnesser. Integration facilitator.</h2>
        <p>I work with the natural intelligence of your body-mind-soul system — where sensations begin to speak, energy reorganises from the depth, and something deeply resonant in you starts moving through silent presence.</p>
        <p>This work is not about fixing or striving. It's about entering the field where what's true begins to reveal itself, in its own rhythm and time.</p>
        <a href="/draft/about" class="link-arrow">More about my journey &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Subtle? -->
  <section class="why-subtle">
    <div class="why-subtle-inner reveal">
      <blockquote class="why-subtle-quote">
        <p>"Everything starts in a subtle way. Even the biggest change and the biggest emotion, like anger. Even when we lash out to someone, there has been a subtle point before where we started — maybe some heat in our belly or some tingling in our hands. And even when deciding to leave a country, to move country, that big decision — at some point, there was a subtle sense of wanting to go somewhere else, of feeling like the right place is somewhere else. I have found that, tuning into the subtle sense when it first appears or whenever we pause and tune into our senses, there is so much power and clarity and goodness that can be unraveled and unfolded through staying with these subtle senses."</p>
        <cite>— Kaja</cite>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Philosophy / Signal Pool -->
  <section class="philosophy" id="philosophy">
    <div class="philosophy-inner">
      <h2 class="text-center reveal">What if everything we need is already here?</h2>
      <p class="text-center philosophy-sub reveal" data-delay="100">Subtle Somatics is not technique — it is cartography for the landscapes beneath language. Here, the body is not analyzed, but deeply and attentively listened to — each sensation a doorway, each holding a request for recognition.</p>
      <div class="pillars">
        <div class="pillar reveal" data-delay="0">
          <div class="pillar-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2">
              <circle cx="24" cy="24" r="16" />
              <circle cx="24" cy="24" r="10" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span class="pillar-num">01</span>
          <h3>An encounter</h3>
          <p>Truly getting to know the thoughts, emotions and sensations you have moment to moment.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pillar reveal" data-delay="150">
          <div class="pillar-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2">
              <path d="M24 6 C24 6 14 18 14 28 C14 34.6 18.5 40 24 40 C29.5 40 34 34.6 34 28 C34 18 24 6 24 6Z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span class="pillar-num">02</span>
          <h3>An unfolding</h3>
          <p>Experiencing your vast inner resourcefulness — in the form of strength, love, presence and more.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pillar reveal" data-delay="300">
          <div class="pillar-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2">
              <path d="M6 24 C12 18 18 30 24 24 C30 18 36 30 42 24" />
              <path d="M6 24 C12 30 18 18 24 24 C30 30 36 18 42 24" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span class="pillar-num">03</span>
          <h3>An integration</h3>
          <p>Connecting into deeper coherence, alignment and embodiment of your innate wholeness.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services -->
  <section class="section" id="services">
    <p class="eyebrow text-center reveal">Two pathways, one intention</p>
    <h2 class="text-center reveal" data-delay="100" style="margin-bottom:3rem">Services</h2>
    <div class="services-grid">
      <a href="/draft/coaching" class="service-card card-shine reveal" data-delay="0">
        <div class="service-img"><img src="/images/subtle-coaching.png" alt="Subtle Coaching" /></div>
        <div class="service-body">
          <h3>Subtle Coaching</h3>
          <p>Meet yourself where you are in life — at the depth where you are vastly resourced to be with life's complexity. Through deepening self-contact, you begin to encounter the vast resources beneath habitual patterns.</p>
          <span class="link-arrow">Explore Coaching &rarr;</span>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a href="/draft/spinal-energetics" class="service-card card-shine reveal" data-delay="150">
        <div class="service-img"><img src="/images/spinal-energetics.png" alt="Spinal Energetics" /></div>
        <div class="service-body">
          <h3>Spinal Energetics</h3>
          <p>A subtle-and-powerful modality combining sound, touch, movement and music to relax the nervous system and connect you deeper with your innate qualities of strength, love, radiance and trust.</p>
          <span class="link-arrow">Explore Spinal Energetics &rarr;</span>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What to expect -->
  <section class="expect">
    <div class="expect-inner">
      <h2 class="text-center reveal">What to expect</h2>
      <p class="text-center expect-sub reveal" data-delay="100">Each step unfolds at its own pace — no rushing, no forcing.</p>
      <div class="expect-grid reveal" data-delay="200">
        <div class="expect-item">
          <span class="expect-num">01</span>
          <h4>Discovery Call</h4>
          <p>A free conversation to sense into whether this work resonates. I'll listen to what's alive for you, and together we'll feel into the right next step.</p>
          <p class="expect-detail">~20 min &middot; Free</p>
        </div>
        <div class="expect-connector" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="connector-line"></div>
          <div class="connector-dot"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="expect-item">
          <span class="expect-num">02</span>
          <h4>Your Session</h4>
          <p>Each session meets you exactly where you are. Whether coaching, spinal energetics, or both — the body leads, and I follow.</p>
          <p class="expect-detail">~60 min &middot; &euro;130</p>
        </div>
        <div class="expect-connector" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="connector-line"></div>
          <div class="connector-dot"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="expect-item">
          <span class="expect-num">03</span>
          <h4>Integration</h4>
          <p>Deeper transformation unfolds over time. A series of sessions supports sustained embodiment of your wholeness.</p>
          <p class="expect-detail">Series of 5 &middot; at your own pace</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Poetic break -->
  <section class="poetic-break">
    <blockquote class="reveal">
      <p class="gradient-text">To practice subtle somatics is to return to the body not as vessel, but as a field — alive, aware, and already knowing.</p>
    </blockquote>
  </section>

  <!-- Image break -->
  <section class="image-break">
    <img src="/images/kaja-secondary.png" alt="Kaja — presence and embodiment" />
    <div class="ib-overlay"></div>
  </section>

  <!-- Booking -->
  <section class="section booking-section" id="booking">
    <div class="booking-inner reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow text-center">Take the first step</p>
      <h2 class="text-center">Book Your Discovery Call</h2>
      <p class="text-center booking-sub">A free, no-commitment conversation to sense into whether this work resonates with you.</p>
      <div class="cal-embed-wrapper">
        <iframe src="https://cal.com/subtlesomatics/discovery" style="width:100%;height:700px;border:none;" loading="lazy" title="Book a discovery call with Subtle Somatics"></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact -->
  <section class="section" id="contact">
    <div class="contact-grid">
      <div class="contact-text reveal-left">
        <p class="eyebrow">Get in Touch</p>
        <h2>Ready to begin?</h2>
        <p>I'd love to have you and feel honoured to serve you — just where you are.</p>
        <div class="contact-details">
          <div class="contact-item">
            <h4>Email</h4>
            <a href="mailto:connect@subtlesomatics.space">connect@subtlesomatics.space</a>
          </div>
          <div class="contact-item">
            <h4>Sessions</h4>
            <p>Online (Zoom) &amp; in person</p>
          </div>
          <div class="contact-item">
            <h4>Location</h4>
            <p>Vienna, Austria</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <form class="contact-form reveal-right" action="https://formsubmit.co/connect@subtlesomatics.space" method="POST">
        <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="New message from subtlesomatics.space (draft)" />
        <input type="hidden" name="_captcha" value="false" />
        <input type="hidden" name="_next" value="https://subtlesomatics.space/draft" />
        <input type="text" name="_honey" style="display:none" />
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="name">Your name</label>
          <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="Your name" />
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="email">Email <span class="required">*</span></label>
          <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="your@email.com" required />
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="message">Message <span class="required">*</span></label>
          <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5" placeholder="What's alive for you right now?" required></textarea>
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-filled">Send Message</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>

</DraftLayout>

<style>
  /* ===== Hero ===== */
  .hero { position: relative; min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; overflow: hidden; }
  .hero-bg { position: absolute; inset: 0; }
  .hero-bg img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; transform-origin: center top; transform: scale(1.1); will-change: transform; }
  .hero-overlay { position: absolute; inset: 0; background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(13,13,15,0.7) 0%, rgba(13,13,15,0.4) 40%, rgba(13,13,15,0.75) 100%); }
  .hero-content { position: relative; z-index: 1; max-width: 700px; padding: 2rem; margin-left: 8%; margin-top: 4rem; }
  .hero-eyebrow { font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 0.25em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .hero h1 { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .hero-sub { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; max-width: 550px; }
  .hero-actions { display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }

  /* Hero entrance animation */
  .hero-anim {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(20px) scale(0.98);
    animation: heroFadeIn 0.8s ease forwards;
  }
  .hero-anim[data-anim-order="1"] { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
  .hero-anim[data-anim-order="2"] { animation-delay: 0.5s; }
  .hero-anim[data-anim-order="3"] { animation-delay: 0.8s; }
  .hero-anim[data-anim-order="4"] { animation-delay: 1.1s; }
  @keyframes heroFadeIn {
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0) scale(1); }
  }

  /* Scroll indicator */
  .scroll-indicator {
    position: absolute; bottom: 2rem; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 0.3rem;
    color: var(--text-muted); z-index: 2;
    animation: scrollBounce 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  .scroll-text {
    font-size: 0.65rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  @keyframes scrollBounce {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0); }
    50% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(8px); }
  }

  /* ===== Shared ===== */
  .eyebrow { font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.25em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }

  /* ===== About intro ===== */
  .about-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.4fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: center; }
  .about-image img { border-radius: 2px; box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); }
  .about-text h2 { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.2rem); line-height: 1.3; }
  .about-text p { margin-bottom: 1.2rem; color: var(--text-secondary); }
  .link-arrow { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--accent); display: inline-block; margin-top: 0.5rem; }
  .link-arrow:hover { color: var(--accent-light); }

  /* ===== Why Subtle ===== */
  .why-subtle {
    background: var(--bg-warm);
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .why-subtle-inner { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .why-subtle-quote p {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 2.2vw, 1.55rem);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: none;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .why-subtle-quote cite {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-style: normal;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--accent);
    text-align: right;
  }

  /* ===== Philosophy ===== */
  .philosophy { background: var(--bg-surface); padding: 6rem 2rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .philosophy-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .philosophy h2 { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-style: italic; }
  .philosophy-sub { color: var(--text-secondary); max-width: 650px; margin: 0 auto 4rem; }
  .pillars { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 3rem; }
  .pillar { padding: 2rem; border-left: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .pillar-icon { color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 1rem; opacity: 0.7; }
  .pillar-num { font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 2.5rem; display: block; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: var(--text-muted); }
  .pillar h3 { font-style: italic; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .pillar p { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.95rem; }

  /* ===== Services ===== */
  .services-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
  .service-card { display: block; background: var(--bg-surface); overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid var(--border); transition: border-color 0.3s, transform 0.3s; text-decoration: none; }
  .service-card:hover { border-color: var(--border-hover); transform: translateY(-4px); }
  .service-img img { width: 100%; height: 260px; object-fit: cover; filter: brightness(0.85); transition: filter 0.3s; }
  .service-card:hover .service-img img { filter: brightness(1); }
  .service-body { padding: 2rem; }
  .service-body h3 { margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--text-primary); }
  .service-body p { margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text-secondary); }
  .service-body .link-arrow { margin-top: 0.5rem; }

  /* ===== What to expect ===== */
  .expect { background: var(--bg-warm); padding: 6rem 2rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .expect-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .expect h2 { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .expect-sub { color: var(--text-muted); margin: 0 auto 3rem; font-style: italic; }
  .expect-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr auto 1fr;
    gap: 0;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .expect-item { padding: 2rem 1.5rem; border: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .expect-num { font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 2rem; color: var(--accent); display: block; margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }
  .expect-item h4 { font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 1.3rem; margin-bottom: 0.8rem; }
  .expect-item p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text-secondary); }
  .expect-detail { font-size: 0.8rem !important; color: var(--accent) !important; margin-top: 1rem; letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .expect-connector {
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    padding-top: 3rem;
    width: 60px;
  }
  .connector-line {
    width: 100%; height: 1px;
    background: var(--accent);
    opacity: 0.4;
    position: relative;
  }
  .connector-dot {
    width: 6px; height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--accent);
    position: absolute;
    left: 50%; top: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
  }
  .expect-connector { position: relative; }
  .connector-dot {
    position: absolute;
    left: 50%; top: 3rem;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
  }

  /* ===== Poetic break ===== */
  .poetic-break { padding: 5rem 2rem; text-align: center; background: var(--bg-deep); }
  .poetic-break blockquote { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .poetic-break p {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 2.5vw, 1.8rem);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: none;
  }

  /* ===== Image break ===== */
  .image-break { position: relative; height: 50vh; overflow: hidden; }
  .image-break img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; filter: brightness(0.7); }
  .ib-overlay { position: absolute; inset: 0; background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(13,13,15,0.1), rgba(13,13,15,0.4)); }

  /* ===== Booking ===== */
  .booking-section { background: var(--bg-surface); border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .booking-inner { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .booking-sub { color: var(--text-secondary); margin: 1rem auto 2.5rem; }
  .cal-embed-wrapper {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--bg-elevated);
  }

  /* ===== Contact ===== */
  .contact-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: start; }
  .contact-text h2 { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .contact-text > p { margin-bottom: 2rem; color: var(--text-secondary); }
  .contact-details { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem; }
  .contact-item h4 { font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }
  .contact-item p, .contact-item a { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text-secondary); }
  .contact-form { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.2rem; }
  .form-group { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.4rem; }
  .form-group label { font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-muted); }
  .required { color: var(--accent); }
  .form-group input, .form-group textarea {
    font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 1rem; padding: 0.85rem 1rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--bg-surface);
    color: var(--text-primary); transition: border-color 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s; font-weight: 300;
  }
  .form-group input:focus, .form-group textarea:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: var(--accent);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px var(--accent-glow), 0 0 16px var(--accent-glow);
  }
  .form-group textarea { resize: vertical; min-height: 100px; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-content { margin-left: 0; }
    .about-grid, .services-grid, .pillars, .contact-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .expect-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; }
    .expect-connector { display: none; }
    .image-break { height: 35vh; }
    .scroll-indicator { display: none; }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .hero-anim { opacity: 1; transform: none; animation: none; }
    .scroll-indicator { animation: none; }
  }
</style>
